    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing, it's not just being exhausted. it's that there's nothing left to even try. i feel like the damage is just too deep. like some people are born with a certain capacity to heal and i just don't have it. it's like a fundamental flaw in my wiring. how can you say there's always a new approach when it feels like the core of me is just... gone?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
